German Pancakes

Vegetarian

1::cups::flour
2::cups::milk
3::None::eggs
1::tablespoons::vegetable oil
None::None::Cooking spray

Mix all ingredients with electric mixer. Spray pan(s) with cooking spray. Pour small amount of batter in center of pan and twirl until batter is spread all around the pan. Should have a thin layer of batter across the whole pan. Brown and turn. When done, spread butter on and sprinkle sugar, roll and sprinkle more sugar.
